Implement a HUD designer utility:
 - The HUD designer should have "standard" components:
   - Text label component.
   - Decoration component (?).
 - Utility to convert a variable to a number label HUD designer component.
 - Utility to convert a variable to a time formatted label HUD designer component.
 - Utility to convert a camera angle to a compass HUD designer component.

Refactor Utilities to be a separate entity class.

Pause / Unpause Commands provided to the Command Registry:
 - GERALD
 - Lifts
 - Enemies
 - Timer

Utility to invoke pause / unpause on all "pausables" from a key press event.
Add zone context awareness to lift set - hide and stop lifts on zone exit, reset and start lifts on zone entry.
Add zone context awareness to enemy set - hide and stop enemies on zone exit, reset and start enemies on zone entry.
Lifts should provide activate / deactivate commands for each lift type to the Command Registry.
Block set should provide customizable set of activate / deactivate commands to the Command Registry.
Add condition configuration to block elements.
Block set should provide a configuration for commands to execute on each switch type.
Utility to implement Spindizzy switch logic (provide switch commands to registry, which invoke appropriate commands on blocks and lifts)

